graphql.query:
query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	cciGetContacts (query: $query)
	{
		id
		tenantCode
		systemName
		roleName
		name
		surname
		email
		mobile
		area
		hasConsentEmail
		hasConsentMobile
		isActive
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	cciFindContact (query: $query)
	{
		id
		tenantCode
		systemName
		roleName
		name
		surname
		email
		mobile
		area
		hasConsentEmail
		hasConsentMobile
		isActive
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

query ($id:ID)
{
	cciFindContactById (id:$id)
	{
		id
		tenantCode
		systemName
		roleName
		name
		surname
		email
		mobile
		area
		hasConsentEmail
		hasConsentMobile
		isActive
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($payload:CciUpdateContactInput!)
{
	cciUpdateContact (payload:$payload)
	{
		id
		tenantCode
		systemName
		roleName
		name
		surname
		email
		mobile
		area
		hasConsentEmail
		hasConsentMobile
		isActive
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($id:ID!)
{
	cciDeleteContactById (id:$id)
	{
		id
		tenantCode
		systemName
		roleName
		name
		surname
		email
		mobile
		area
		hasConsentEmail
		hasConsentMobile
		isActive
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	cciDeleteContacts (query: $query)
	{
		id
		tenantCode
		systemName
		roleName
		name
		surname
		email
		mobile
		area
		hasConsentEmail
		hasConsentMobile
		isActive
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}
